text: Mazharul Haque Prodhan (born January 1, 1953) is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the incumbent Member of Parliament of Panchagarh-1. ==Career== Prodhan was elected to parliament from Panchagarh-1 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate 30 December 2018. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:9th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:1953 births
title: Mazharul Haque Prodhan
